
                               ept-get

ept-get is a software which allows to recoursively remove software on gentoo linux.

It might also be useful for those, who already familiar with apt-get usage

ept-get depends on epkg ( epkg.sf.net )

Usage:

ept-get remove packagename

Removes package and all packages which depends on that package

ept-get install package

Installs package (currently this one just calls emerge)

ept-get update (currently calls emerge --sunc)

ept-get --download-only package (calls emerge -f package)
